features: 【Specifications】Material: PU Leather, Foam, Metal, Nylon, Plywood, PP; Color: Black; Overall Dimensions: 28” W × 28” D × (43.5-47)” H; Seat Height: 19.5-23.2”; Maximum Weight Capacity: 300 lb

【Strong Solid Construction】This mid-back executive chair boasts a CARB P2-compliant plywood frame, heavy-duty steel base and smooth-rolling nylon casters, which combine to provide great stability and mobility. With the SGS-approved gas lift, the chair has a weight capacity of 300 lbs and offers a sturdy foundation for enduring comfort.

【Large Cushioned Seat & Neck Support】The seat measures 20.3" (W) x 19.5" (D) and is padded with 4cm thick high-resiliency foam, which accommodates different body types and provides a more relaxed sitting experience. The raised headrest provides a soft, pillow-like surface for the neck and shoulders when you lean back and relax.

【Comfy Mid-to-Low Back Support】The backrest of this executive office chair features thick segmented cushions, offering sufficient mid-to-low back support and cushy comfort to make to make long hours at work easier. The built-in lumbar support can be effortlessly adjusted to better align with the spine, alleviating lower back stress and tension.

【Convenient Adjustment】The gaming chair's pneumatic gas cylinder allows for easy seat height adjustment and rocking back. Turn the knob on the right side of the seat to inflate the lumbar area, providing efficient support for your lower back. Multiple adjustments empower you to customize your sitting experience and boost productivity.
